{
  "stem": "27748.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I came with these assumptions that my childhood would be returned to me, and it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I went to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the house was totally renovated into modern-- what I think of as modern American suburbia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You could have walked into any house here and be the same, the same furnishings, the television, of course running water by then, electricity, and all the appliances.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You could be in modern suburban house, totally different from the past, except that the attic and the cellar had not yet been renovated and they were still the same.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I sort of assumed they would come back to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But anyway, so I went to the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I went to the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The school was closed, so we looked-- we looked in through the windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Jewish cemetery was in beautiful condition, beautiful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The lawns were beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The stones were all straight and erect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, apparently the German government had allocated money to keep the Jewish cemeteries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was in beautiful condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked around in the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and all of a sudden, I was in front of what was formerly a synagogue and was now a bank.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there I stood and I was unable to move.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was unable to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remembered-- I guess in retrospect maybe I was remembering the desecration of the Torahs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But here-- and I was this totally non-practicing Jew for 25 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here the synagogue wrenched me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was unable to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the only building that was available to me I couldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, the other phenomena during that day, in the afternoon, we were invited to an old lady's home over coffee and cake.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
